1.MUST_REVALIDATE
 check if the cache expired ,if yes ,lock the redis ,then revalidate it 

2. STALE_WHILE_REVALIDATE
check if the cach is expired ,serve stale until the period ,lock it after the stale period ,then revalidate

3. STALE_IF_ERROR 
 a. Independent Scheduler check for health
 b. Ping the origin ,If the server is down ,serve stale
 c. The scheduler sets the internal state of the server 
 d. If the server is down check via internal state ,serve stale
 e. If its up ,get the data.
 f. The check should be
    if origin healthy and current time > TTL  
        ping the origin
    else
        serve stale 
